ence\nof other new physics at the energy scale ranging from $10^7 {\\rm GeV}$ to\n$10^{11} {\\rm GeV}$. Collider tests of our explanations are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Dec 2017 17:27:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 06:12:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2018 02:02:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-04"}
