-critical\ntemperature the system exhibits standard behavior as for ordinary\none-dimensional spin models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Dec 2017 11:18:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2018 13:01:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Jun 2018 12:37:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-18"}
