g the geodynamics of ice-rich planets f,\ng, and h requires more sophisticated modeling that can self-consistently\nbalance heat production and transport in both rock and ice layers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Dec 2017 12:34:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Jan 2018 07:42:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-30"}
